description: The seed of varieties of agricultural and plant species and varieties of vegetable species that are published in the EU level common catalogue is subject to no marketing restrictions with the Community.  Publication in the catalogue must be approved as fulfilling minimum requirements laid down in legislation.  Data is published on the contents of the catalogues for agricultural and vegetal species and maintainers with details of the reference list.
